  • All Classes Class Summary Exception Summary 
    Class Description
    CanNotMillException
    Exception raises if mill is impossible due to missing M commands
    CNC_Machine
    The class serves as CPU to coordinate all tasks of the CNC milling machine.
    CommandProcessor
    The class is used to provide several functions: Sort commandJson, store commands in workList and uiLog and also makes them available for the logger to write them into the logFile
    CoolingSimulator
    Class needed to simulate the cooling function on the UI.
    Coordinates
    Class used to store coordinates and regarding information needed for the UI.
    Drill
    Class for calculating all drill coordinates triggered by g-codes.
    DrillPointer
    Class is needed to simulate the drill on the UI
    ExceptionHandler
    Class that includes handling of occured errors.
    HomePoint
    Class for displaying HomePoint
    Logger
    Class responsible for storing log data in the file system
    Main
    Main Class of JavaFx Application.
    OutOfWorksurfaceException
    Exception raises if a calculated point or the target point of draw line method is outside the worksurface.
    SimulateMill
    Class for simulating the drilling of previously calculated coordinates coordinates have already been calculated in Drill
    UIController
    Class for controlling the user Interface of the cnc machine simulator Ui design is done using fxml
    UndefinedAngleException
    Exception raised when calculation of an angle is impossible.
    WorkSurface
    Class for worksurface off CNC_Machine this is the drawing area
    WrongCommandException
    Exception raised if an user uploads a json-file containing wrong commands.
